    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597790/extras/2790586e580d62e7296a8e4c5cb6ab5c.poster.avif?t=1771855363\" width=616 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597790/extras/2790586e580d62e7296a8e4c5cb6ab5c.webm?t=1771855363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597790/extras/2790586e580d62e7296a8e4c5cb6ab5c.mp4?t=1771855363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>&gt; /app/1184810/Mainframe_Defenders &lt;</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>《主机保卫队》：Meltdown - Prologue</strong> 是回合制策略游戏《<strong>主机保卫队</strong>》的免费试玩版。在复杂的策略游戏中操控由4种原型机组成的部队，同时体验毫不逊色的游戏操作元素。设法克服装备的限制与不足，创造强大战队。用各种战术消灭对手：烧毁敌军，腐蚀歼灭，吸收伤害再回敬给对方。不要只依靠单单一种策略——单一策略很容易被敌人破解。凭你调遣的有：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">﻿﻿24个机甲中的6个，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">﻿190件装备中的90个，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">﻿3个行动中的1个。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597790/extras/715229907ccdb6537db669b2f5d0aa8f.poster.avif?t=1771855363\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597790/extras/715229907ccdb6537db669b2f5d0aa8f.webm?t=1771855363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597790/extras/715229907ccdb6537db669b2f5d0aa8f.mp4?t=1771855363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597790/extras/e170f91e21109af24693ed8883faa860.poster.avif?t=1771855363\" width=600 height=76 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597790/extras/e170f91e21109af24693ed8883faa860.webm?t=1771855363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>* 复古风格：</strong>80年代绘图结合时尚复古音乐。<br><br><strong>* 多种战术：</strong>用过热杀死机器人，用子弹狂射，用强力射击将其一击毙命，或用状态效果使其瘫痪——游戏在设计时考虑了许多可行的策略。<br><br><strong>* 组建你的部队：</strong>与必须组合套牌的纸牌游戏类似，在《<strong>主机保卫队</strong>》中，你必须将具有独特属性的装备组合在一起以创建无敌部队。通过强大的策略来弥补装备缺陷！<br><br><strong>* 独特的对手：</strong>请注意，敌人不会停滞不前。每个单位都有在部队中发挥独特作用，每个单位都有能力应对某些策略。运用策略选择目标，出奇制胜，不然就有被打败的危险。<br><br><strong>* 程序等级：</strong>手工制作的房间与程序级别的生成相结合。不同任务有不同的目标，并有独特的条件。接受挑战，还是被敌人远远甩在身后？<br><br><strong>* 递进系统：</strong>游戏不会以一胜一负结束！解锁新的单位，每个单位都有一套独特的升级和起始物品。解锁新物品以支持你的新策略。了解“占星师”中的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597790/extras/2ad78f6b2cef9e7d4b19fcd307c90c86.poster.avif?t=1771855363\" width=600 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597790/extras/2ad78f6b2cef9e7d4b19fcd307c90c86.webm?t=1771855363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597790/extras/2ad78f6b2cef9e7d4b19fcd307c90c86.mp4?t=1771855363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597790/extras/261ea5